name: SF Pro Rounded
description:
Dynamic Type Collection


This simple collection contains all the dynamic type sizes for SF Pro Rounded in 4 weights: Regular, Medium, Semibold, and Bold.


The purpose of this is to provide a singular set of type sizes for SF Pro Rounded that matches the font sizes used in an iOS app.


Updates

08/25/21 - Added correct tracking (line-spacing) values according to documentation.
